<p>Building expertise and trust across all stages of the customer journey to enhance category and topic authority.</p>
</div>
<div class="case-study"><h3>In Practice</h3><p>A B2B platform company tracked a single metric throughout their AEO engagement: how often sales reps heard "I already know who you are" at the start of a first call. Before AEO, it was rare. Twelve months into the program, it had become regular — a qualitative signal that decision-makers were encountering their brand in AI-generated research before the sales process began.</p></div></section>
